{"tid":12070,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"油麻地麻麻地拉麵","createTime":"2016-11-29T13:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T10:30:09.000Z","uid":4806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f07bc06dac7cd41f137ffbc2d15b9dca4b70ec6","tid":12070,"uid":4806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:37:08.000Z","msg":"本身小弟就係一個拉麵控<br />\n有日經過呢間見咁q多人排隊<br />\n就諗住實無死啦<br />\nOpenrice search過都有300幾正評<br />\n<br />\n等左半個鐘到<br />\n叫左個櫻花蝦+蝦湯拉麵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9h3850e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9h3850e.jpg&h=cd306fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎到賣相都唔錯<br />\n屌你 點知食落勁似公仔麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n湯又無味 係叫聞到少少蝦味<br />\n舊肉又無乜味咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係759一包包d拉麵仲好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人覺得香港拉麵排名：<br />\n周X&gt;拉X來&gt;廣島霸X&gt;隱X拉麵&gt;混X拉麵<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位巴打有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96313810dee73bc107084a2efcc3176c57bf5387","tid":12070,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:39:44.000Z","msg":"全部名都唔開<br />\n都唔知你講邊X間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a71c3a99773488a511a00721e36ec57b884a218","tid":12070,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:43:42.000Z","msg":"以前有 三八拉麵 (得日文名) 好好食 尖沙咀 不過執左幾年 <br />\n而家香港d拉麵店真係好一般 有時去下恒豐食下囉 <br />\n有d想試去上水元朗試山下<br />\n前排試左間 都唔錯 但醒唔起邊度食 <br />\n西九間沾麵ok 不過紅左冇去 日日隊咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1431bc93f68b4c4448fa54b41702f98dea575d11","tid":12070,"uid":13948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前有 三八拉麵 (得日文名) 好好食 尖沙咀 不過執左幾年 <br />\n而家香港d拉麵店真係好一般 有時去下恒豐食下囉 <br />\n有d想試去上水元朗試山下<br />\n前排試左間 都唔錯 但醒唔起邊度食 <br />\n西九間沾麵ok 不過紅左冇去 日日隊咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n山下真心難食，西九果間都係麻麻"},{"pid":"cec3300d3c69ed959a629f52ac9341df06156004","tid":12070,"uid":4806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:01:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全部名都唔開<br />\n都唔知你講邊X間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開左名又俾人話打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ba51a53d18da8142cd6fb127a54b6a2e2a1bda","tid":12070,"uid":4806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:02:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前有 三八拉麵 (得日文名) 好好食 尖沙咀 不過執左幾年 <br />\n而家香港d拉麵店真係好一般 有時去下恒豐食下囉 <br />\n有d想試去上水元朗試山下<br />\n前排試左間 都唔錯 但醒唔起邊度食 <br />\n西九間沾麵ok 不過紅左冇去 日日隊咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n山下真心難食，西九果間都係麻麻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西九個間咪隱X，我覺得幾好食，不過真係勁多人排隊on9"},{"pid":"f825085214b0808b118e0aa9335c8f4ee132d5e9","tid":12070,"uid":14884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:07:26.000Z","msg":"知邊間，櫻花蝦真係麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0f34b65a313121a206cafe7adff0544e4014ae","tid":12070,"uid":7246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"山下以前真係好食 而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35580c00ea0271dd5ffcba558de096cc5e746c4d","tid":12070,"uid":43585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T19:57:46.000Z","msg":"橫崗 早幾日食過 味道真係麻麻 但有擦擦卡 擦中30蚊 <br />\n<br />\n50蚊碗又屌佢唔落"},{"pid":"543cf3e6fe51b65434d67225cfd3203672463475","tid":12070,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:00:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身小弟就係一個拉麵控<br />\n有日經過呢間見咁q多人排隊<br />\n就諗住實無死啦<br />\nOpenrice search過都有300幾正評<br />\n<br />\n等左半個鐘到<br />\n叫左個櫻花蝦+蝦湯拉麵<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/9h3850e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9h3850e.jpg&h=43085bc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎到賣相都唔錯<br />\n屌你 點知食落勁似公仔麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n湯又無味 係叫聞到少少蝦味<br />\n舊肉又無乜味咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係759一包包d拉麵仲好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人覺得香港拉麵排名：<br />\n周X&amp;gt;拉X來&amp;gt;廣島霸X&amp;gt;隱X拉麵&amp;gt;混X拉麵<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位巴打有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打開名分享下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbb053a38eb8f373373eaf9e2299fe7b5c59c5c","tid":12070,"uid":42448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:05:37.000Z","msg":"有無食過旺角/荃灣漁場台X?"},{"pid":"3392f80e9531620ffe8d3e5559330d5e065afe5b","tid":12070,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:13:54.000Z","msg":"大勝軒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7702c5e1dd3876aa36112d8d522ad787f425da","tid":12070,"uid":26082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:15:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前有 三八拉麵 (得日文名) 好好食 尖沙咀 不過執左幾年 <br />\n而家香港d拉麵店真係好一般 有時去下恒豐食下囉 <br />\n有d想試去上水元朗試山下<br />\n前排試左間 都唔錯 但醒唔起邊度食 <br />\n西九間沾麵ok 不過紅左冇去 日日隊咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n元朗山下試過 唔掂"},{"pid":"b68b0c3e8567faa9c4234f1def5769ecb74e4158","tid":12070,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:21:11.000Z","msg":"長浜no.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898284a493e70d9f213a4fe6a1cfacc6d7c90a45","tid":12070,"uid":42710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:35:49.000Z","msg":"我知你講邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前好食，依家越做越垃圾<br />\n早兩個月都排過一次，都排左成45分鐘<br />\n食完決定以後唔再幫襯<br />\n佢啲味道真係買包拉麵都煮到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔值得我排咁耐隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人覺得台風同拉麵來好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c10fb6b9436130b5bba2319713cb3d62c7468c6","tid":12070,"uid":31946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:35:50.000Z","msg":"香港拉面 無彩上排名<br />\n<br />\n混亂飽肚就得 味道真係麻麻 反而榜上有名<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719aab78c32b93b516bb1d63238249df93cfd396","tid":12070,"uid":31946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:37:39.000Z","msg":"暫時食過最好食既拉面（香港） 一定係彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然越做越差 不過都仲係最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a020badabaaf68abf91c5cc283d5b3bd24ef9841","tid":12070,"uid":4806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:18:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無食過旺角/荃灣漁場台X?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有呀，我覺得都還可以，但印象唔深刻"},{"pid":"75e2114ec04a811b3b7c3e65b1370a5b86947a9e","tid":12070,"uid":4806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:19:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港拉面 無彩上排名<br />\n<br />\n混亂飽肚就得 味道真係麻麻 反而榜上有名<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係wor, 唔記得有彩，食過一次，d麵有d似意粉，不過個湯幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋好記得個日本師傅好似劉松仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5f5473c75b28b8dc77cf206631736686fc12f7","tid":12070,"uid":4806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:20:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暫時食過最好食既拉面（香港） 一定係彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然越做越差 不過都仲係最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得香港最好食都係中環間周X<br />\n沾麵湯帶有少少醋酸味，唔會有「漏」既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有帆立貝油撈麵都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54ad4dd798a8efa17b86c62f86bf3e9a344a7c5","tid":12070,"uid":33568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>山下以前真係好食 而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未開分店之前有心好多 食落真係有唔同"},{"pid":"84882e221bce08af406d4a480130e1635444d87f","tid":12070,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:02:43.000Z","msg":"價錢如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cb81722ee02c9fb91249573a64842cd15a4eff","tid":12070,"uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:05:41.000Z","msg":"周x拉麵好難食，要食沾麵。<br />\n拉麵灣仔有兩間都有個虎字，最好食<br />\n餃子係奧運站小林"},{"pid":"e539ddd13d6a9c0ed956ae978d97f9434c8cf632","tid":12070,"uid":34080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:06:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d910ed5ab126b1d5f710b5bd88d51bcc8357816","tid":12070,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:07:03.000Z","msg":"霸馬，拉都來覺得算好食"}]}